ized today's file with a \\\"RESUMING\\\" entry to bridge the 5-hour gap since our last interaction.\\n*   [ ] **Project Start:** Draft the `FACTORY_V2_APP_BRIEF` to codify the MCP and Skill Registry requirements.\\n*   [ ] **Data Architecture:** Define the `DATA_CONTRACT.md` for the agent-to-skill checkbox mapping.\\n\\nReady to start the **FACTORY_V2_APP_BRIEF**, or should we look at the MCP research first?\"}],\"role\":\"model\"},\"intermediate_data\":{\"tool_uses\":[{\"id\":\"adk-90333fc0-ae4f-447a-bad3-837c77dbf0b0\",\"args\":{\"skill_name\":\"SESSION_MEMORY_SKILL\"},\"name\":\"invoke_skill\"},{\"id\":\"adk-117f2a42-83f8-490d-b80d-fd1113a91147\",\"args\":{\"days\":7},\"name\":\"read_session_memory\"},{\"id\":\"adk-a405e594-7d10-47ff-a42d-51f66d8c8bae\",\"args\":{\"skill_name\":\"SESSION_UPDATE_SKILL\"},\"name\":\"invoke_skill\"},{\"id\":\"adk-3ab64a74-f25d-464d-9587-2ba4ee82d3ca\",\"args\":{\"content\":\"### 13:44 \u2014 RESUMING\\n\\n**Context:** Resuming after a ~5-hour gap.\\n**Action:** Restored context from the 08:31 UTC decision regarding Factory Infrastructure V2 (MCP, Open Brain, Managed Skill Registry).\\n**Outcome:** Grounded in current project state.\\n**Next:** Begin drafting the `FACTORY_V2_APP_BRIEF`.\\n\"},\"name\":\"write_session_memory\"}],\"intermediate_responses\":[]},\"creation_timestamp\":0.0},\"expected_invocation\":{\"invocation_id\":\"inv_skill_01\",\"user_content\":{\"parts\":[{\"video_metadata\":null,\"thought\":null,\"inline_data\":null,\"file_data\":null,\"thought_signature\":null,\"code_execution_result\":null,\"executable_code\":null,\"function_call\":null,\"function_response\":null,\"text\":\"How should I update the session file?\"}],\"role\":\"user\"},\"final_response\":{\"parts\":[{\"video_metadata\":null,\"thought\":null,\"inline_data\":null,\"file_data\":null,\"thought_signature\":null,\"code_execution_result\":null,\"executable_code\":null,\"function_call\":null,\"function_response\":null,\"text\":\"\"}],\"role\":\"model\"},\